BEGIN
   Start ESP32 Web Server
   Serve index.html + chart.min.js
   Fetch /data endpoint from ESP32 every few seconds
   Update Charts with new values:
       Chart1: Voltage vs Time
       Chart2: Current vs Time
       Chart3: Power vs Time
       Chart4: Lux vs Time
       Chart5: Temp vs Time
   Update Health Bar in Solar Panel State tab
END
BEGIN
   IF new firmware uploaded THEN
        Write firmware to flash memory
        Reboot ESP32
   ELSE
        Continue normal monitoring
   ENDIF
END